* Iron kep on walking, putting up a wall where her feelings won't be able to 
get out anymore.
But then she stopped, knowing for a fact that she couldn't just turn her 
back and walk away from this city idea, letting everyone else work while she 
went off to pout.*

" But when you get ready to build, call me."

* And from there she continued walking.*
